## Phase 7 — Improvement

### Lessons Learned & Recommendations

| Gap Identified | Recommended Control |
|---|---|
| Unrestricted PowerShell execution | Enforce Constrained Language Mode or ASR rules |
| No internal network segmentation | Implement host-based firewall rules or NSG policies |
| Scripts downloadable via web requests | Block Invoke-WebRequest to untrusted domains via proxy |
| No alerting on internal port scanning | Build Sentinel rule to alert on high-volume internal failed connections |

**Proposed Detection Rule (Future):**
A Sentinel Scheduled Query Rule could be created using the failed connection aggregation query to automatically alert when any internal IP exceeds a threshold of failed connections within a short window — turning this reactive hunt into a proactive detection.

